<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Hahmlet&family=Noto+Sans+KR&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        html, body {
            font-family: 'Hahmlet', serif;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            background-color: #eee;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .container{
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .container1{
            width: 100em;
            height: 50em;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-evenly;
        }
        .img{
            width: 412px;
            height: 412px;
        }
        .item1{
            width: 5em;
            height: 2.5em;
            font-size: 2em;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
            border-radius: 20px;
        }
        .item2{
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            width: 100em;
            height: 40em;
            background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
            border-radius: 20px;
        }
        .item3{
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 2em;
            width: 20em;
            height: 5em;
        }
        .item4{
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 100em;
            height: 3em;
        }
        input[type=button]{
            font-family: 'Hahmlet', serif;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            width: 5em;
            height: 2em;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: none;
            background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
        }
        input[type=button]:hover{
            font-family: 'Hahmlet', serif;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            width: 5em;
            height: 2em;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: none;
            box-shadow: 2px 2px 2px gray;
            background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
        }
   </style>
    <script>
        function menupage(){
            location.href = "/menu";
        }
    </script>
    <title>Tank Game</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="container1">        
            <div class="item1">
                게임 설명<br>
            </div>
            <div class="item2">
                <div class="item3">
                    W, A, S, D 키로 탱크를 움직일 수 있습니다<br>
                </div>
                <div class="img">
                    <img src="./wasd">
                </div>
                <div class="item3">
                    화살표 키들로 탱크의 총알의 방향을 설정할 수<br>있습니다.<br>
                </div>
                <div class="img">
                    <img src="./arrow">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item4">
                <input type="button" value="돌아가기" onclick="menupage()">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>